Reasoning: The paper discusses the theory of quasi-metric spaces and their applications in similarity measures and searches of biological datasets, specifically nucleotide and protein sequences. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.DS (data structures and algorithms), cs.LG (machine learning), and cs.DB (databases). Additionally, the paper has a focus on biological applications, which could place it in the q-bio sub-categories, such as q-bio.BM (biomolecules) and q-bio.GN (genomics).
